        <abstract> 
<p>Has sent 2d ed. of his book, <hi rend="italic">Werden und Vergehen</hi> [1880]. Notes that book was attacked in Prussian House of Deputies by ultramontane critics of Hermann Müller who had recommended it to his pupils.</p> 
